    <h2>Terms and Conditions</h2>
    <h3>Rescheduling, Substitution and Cancellation Policy</h3>
    <ul>
        <li>
            No charge for substituting students at any time.
        </li>
        <li>
            No charge to reschedule or cancel before 5 business days of class.
        </li>
        <li>
            There is a $<%= Money.new(site(:retake_fee)).to_s %> rescheduling or cancellation fee
            within 3-5 business days from the start of class.
        </li>
        <li>
            No refund or rescheduling permitted within 2 business days of start of
