    <ul>
        <li>
            We do not sell or give away any of your information to any third parties.
        </li>
        <li>
            Your emails and phone numbers are only used in relation to training correspondence.
        </li>
        <li>
            You may receive follow up emails if communication is lost.
        </li>
    </ul>
</div>
